            <title>[OAK-2970] DocumentNodeStoreService doesn&apos;t fully implement a @Modified method</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2970</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;DocumentNodeStoreService&lt;/tt&gt; component uses a &lt;tt&gt;@Modified&lt;/tt&gt; method that picks up changes in couple of configuration properties and ignores the rest.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Based on the comments by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=frm&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;frm&quot;&gt;frm&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2960&quot; title=&quot;SegmentNodeStoreService doesn&amp;#39;t fully implement a @Modified method&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-2960&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-2960&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; the &lt;tt&gt;@Modified&lt;/tt&gt; method should be removed. It is safer to go through a complete deactivation and activation process.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
